<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0,width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>通讯录</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
            p{
                height: 10px;
                background-color: #EFEFF2;
            }
    	body{
    	font-size: 12px;
            font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, STHeiTi, sans-serif;
            background: #EFEFF2;

    	}
        .tit{
            width: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            height: 190px;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }
        .btns{
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btns .btn{
            margin: 16px 30px 0 30px;
            background: #0DA4FF;
            color: 18px;
            line-height: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 6px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
        <p></p>
	<div class="tit">
        <div style="margin:20px 30px 140px 30px;color:#666;font-size:14px;text-align:center;">
            请您在手机→设置→隐私→通讯录中打开“天天分期”应用程序，即可授权您的通讯录
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="btns">
        <div class="btn" tapmode="" onclick="closeWin();">确认</div>
    </div>
</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js">
var closeWin= function(){
		api.closeWin({
	    	name:'contacts',
	    	animation:{
	    		duration:0
	    	}
	    });
    }
</script>
</html>